ChangeLog
=========

.. _v0.3.0:

0.3.0 (unreleased)
------------------

*Bugfix:*

*New:*

    - Accept path-like objects as (https://github.com/rbarrois/aionotify/pull/4)

*Minor Changes:*

    - Use stdlib's ``unittest.IsolatedAsyncioTestCase`` when possible
      (python > 3.7) (from https://github.com/rbarrois/aionotify/pull/15 )

*Removal:*

    - Drop support of Python<3.7 (EoL)
    - Add support for python 3.7, 3.8, 3.9, 3.10

.. _v0.2.0:

0.2.0 (2016-04-04)
------------------

*Bugfix:*

    - Add support for disconnecting watches
    - Fix concurrent events / watch disconnection


.. _v0.1.0:

0.1.0 (2016-04-04)
------------------

*New:*

    - Initial version

